## Executive Summary

Pi has a **three-layer message transformation pipeline** that could serve as foundation for explicit context management and a persistent conversation graph. The session system already implements a tree structure with branching. To achieve full determinism, additional metadata (seed, temperature, hardware quirks) would need to be captured.

