## Key Integration Points for Conversation Graph

### Where Context is Constructed

```
Agent.prompt() / Agent.continue()
    │
    ▼ createContextSnapshot()
    │
    ▼ AgentContext { systemPrompt, messages, tools }
    │
    ▼ agentLoop() / agentLoopContinue()
    │
    ▼ streamAssistantResponse()
    │   ├─ transformContext(messages)     // Optional pre-processing
    │   ├─ convertToLlm(messages)         // AgentMessage → Message
    │   └─ streamSimple(model, context)   // Calls provider
    │
    ▼ transformMessages() inside provider
    │
    ▼ Provider-specific HTTP request
```

### What's Already Captured for Determinism

| Data | Where Stored | Reproducible? |
|------|--------------|---------------|
| Message history | SessionEntry.message | ✅ Yes |
| Model ID | AssistantMessage.model | ✅ Yes |
| Provider | AssistantMessage.provider | ✅ Yes |
| API type | AssistantMessage.api | ✅ Yes |
| Timestamp | AssistantMessage.timestamp | ✅ Yes |
| Usage stats | AssistantMessage.usage | ✅ Yes |
| Response ID | AssistantMessage.responseId | ⚠️ Provider-specific, may enable caching replay |
| Thinking signatures | ThinkingContent.thinkingSignature | ⚠️ Provider-specific, enables thinking replay |

### What's Missing for Full Determinism

| Data | Why Needed | Where to Add |
|------|-----------|--------------|
| Seed | Reproducible sampling | `StreamOptions.seed` → AssistantMessage |
| Temperature | Sampling variance | Already in `StreamOptions`, needs capture in AssistantMessage |
| Top_p, etc. | Other sampling params | `StreamOptions` → AssistantMessage |
| Hardware/driver | GPU non-determinism | Would need external capture |
| Model weights hash | Model version tracking | Would need model registry |
| Provider request ID | Full request tracing | Could capture from API response |

