#### Key APIs Used

```typescript
// Access session manager
const sessionManager = context.sessionManager;
const entries = sessionManager.loadSession(sessionId);

// Access conversion functions
import { convertToLlm } from "@mariozechner/pi-coding-agent";
import { transformMessages } from "@mariozechner/pi-ai/providers";

// Access current agent state
const state = context.agent.state;
const messages = state.messages;

// Subscribe to events for live updates
context.agent.subscribe((event, signal) => {
  if (event.type === "message_end") {
    visualizer.refresh();
  }
});

// Capture provider payloads
const sdk = context.sdk;
sdk.onPayload = (payload, model) => {
  visualizer.capturePayload(payload, model);
};
```

#### Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `message-visualizer:open` | Open visualizer for current session |
| `message-visualizer:entry` | View specific entry by ID |
| `message-visualizer:compare` | Compare layers for selected message |
| `message-visualizer:export` | Export session as JSON |
| `message-visualizer:diff` | Compare two sessions/branches |

