### Data Flow for Visualization

```
Session File (JSONL)
    │
    ▼ SessionManager.loadSession()
    │
SessionEntry[]
    │
    ├─── Direct rendering (Session Layer view)
    │
    ▼ SessionManager.buildSessionContext()
    │
AgentMessage[]
    │
    ├─── Direct rendering (Agent Layer view)
    │
    ▼ convertToLlm()
    │
Message[]
    │
    ├─── Direct rendering (LLM Layer view)
    │
    ▼ transformMessages(model)
    │
Message[] (normalized)
    │
    ▼ Provider-specific conversion
    │
ProviderFormat[]
    │
    └─── Direct rendering (Provider Layer view)
```

