### Features

#### 1. Session Browser
- List all sessions in `~/.pi/agent/sessions/`
- Show session metadata (cwd, start time, model)
- Load and visualize any session

#### 2. Branch Navigation
- Show tree structure of session entries
- Navigate between branches
- Highlight current branch
- Show merge points

#### 3. Content Inspection
- Expand/collapse content blocks
- View images inline (for supported terminals)
- Copy content to clipboard
- View truncated output files

#### 4. Metadata Summary
- Token usage over time
- Model changes
- Thinking level changes
- Compaction events

#### 5. Export & Analysis
- Export to JSON/Markdown
- Generate conversation report
- Compute statistics (turn counts, token totals, etc.)

